SHR DBus Interface Specification

org.shr.phoneuid.PhoneLog

Description

The PhoneLog Interface is used to show the screen with a list of call events (incoming, outgoing, missed) optionally filtered by some criteria.

Namespace

org.shr.phoneuid.PhoneLog

Methods

  • DisplayList

Signals

None

Errors

None

Methods

DisplayList ( a{sv} )

Parameters

a{sv}: filter

List of filter attributes to limit the list of calls to be shown.
